{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/trailer-gundala-tampilkan-asal-usul-sancaka-yang-keras/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Trailer Gundala Tampilkan Asal Usul Sancaka Yang Keras","content":"\n<p>Setelah sekian lama, akhirnya film Gundala garapa Joko Anwar mendapatkan <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SdAhF3NYvk4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"trailer perdana (opens in a new tab)\">trailer perdana</a> serta tanggal rilis!</p>\n\n\n\n<iframe width=\"1280\" height=\"480\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SdAhF3NYvk4\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n\n<p>Film produksi studio Screenplay Films, Legacy Pictures dan\nBumiLangit ini terfokus pada asal usul kemunculan sosok superhero Gundala yang\nmemiliki kekuatan pengendalian listrik. Alter ego dari sang Putra Petir adalah\nSancaka, dan dalam trailer ini kita bisa melihat asal usul karakternya. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53639\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-gundala-tampilkan-asal-usul-sancaka-yang-keras/attachment/01-gundala-trailer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-gundala-trailer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-gundala-trailer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-gundala-trailer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-gundala-trailer.jpg\" alt=\"Sancaka, diperankan Abimana Aryasatya. Sumber: Screenplay Films\" class=\"wp-image-53639\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-gundala-trailer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sancaka, diperankan Abimana Aryasatya. Sumber: Screenplay Films</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di trailer Gundala ini kita bisa melihat masa kecil Sancaka (Muzaki) bersama ayahnya (Rio Dewanto), lalu bagaimana sang ayah tewas di tengah huru hara dan Sancaka cilik harus bertahan hidup di dunia yang sangat keras. Begitu beranjak dewasa pun, Sancaka (Abimana Aryasatya) tak bisa lepas dari kejamnya dunia luar. Klimaksnya tentu saja saat Sancaka disambar petir dan mendapatkan kekuatannya.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: </strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/teaser-gundala-abimana-aryasatya/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Teaser Gundala Terungkap Beserta Pemerannya</strong></a></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53640\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-gundala-tampilkan-asal-usul-sancaka-yang-keras/attachment/02-gundala-trailer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-gundala-trailer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-gundala-trailer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-gundala-trailer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-gundala-trailer.jpg\" alt=\"Pengkor, diperankan Bront Palarae. Sumber: Screenplay Films\" class=\"wp-image-53640\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-gundala-trailer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/02-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Pengkor, diperankan Bront Palarae. Sumber: Screenplay Films</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Di trailer Gundala ini pun ditampilkan sosok Pengkor (Bront Palarae), musuh bebuyutan Gundala. Pengkor pun diperlihatkan masa kecilnya hingga ia beranjak dewasa menjadi seorang criminal mastermind. Dalam satu adegan diperlihatkan Pengkor dan anak buahnya merencanakan sesuatu, dengan latar langit yang dipenuhi kelelawar.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53641\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-gundala-tampilkan-asal-usul-sancaka-yang-keras/attachment/03-gundala-trailer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-gundala-trailer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-gundala-trailer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-gundala-trailer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-gundala-trailer.jpg\" alt=\"Trailer Gundala menunjukkan kelamnya dunia superhero ini. Sumber: Screenplay Films\" class=\"wp-image-53641\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-gundala-trailer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Trailer Gundala menunjukkan kelamnya dunia superhero ini. Sumber: Screenplay Films</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Lewat trailer Gundala ini, Joko Anwar nampaknya ingin fokus menggambarkan seperti apa dunia dalam film Gundala. Bayangkan Indonesia yang dikuasai hukum rimba, dimana kekerasan dan huru hara jadi makanan sehari-hari. Lewat pilihannya ini pula, Joko Anwar juga ingin memberi sinyal bahwa Gundala merupakan sebuah film superhero yang tidak biasa. Aksi baku hantam yang ditampilkan sangat keras dan menggigit. Mungkin salah satu sebabnya karena partisipasi Cecep Arief Rahman sebagai koreografer aksi. Sebab lainnya bisa saja karena di sepanjang trailer dimainkan lagu The End of the World dari Skeeter Davis.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53642\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-gundala-tampilkan-asal-usul-sancaka-yang-keras/attachment/04-gundala-trailer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-gundala-trailer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-gundala-trailer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-gundala-trailer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-gundala-trailer.jpg\" alt=\"Sancaka mengejar “Awang.” Sumber: Screenplay Films\" class=\"wp-image-53642\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-gundala-trailer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/04-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sancaka mengejar “Awang.” Sumber: Screenplay Films</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Satu hal yang menarik dari trailer Gundala ini, adalah potongan adegan dimana Sancaka kecil berlari mengejar kereta. Seorang temannya di atas kereta menyemangati Sancaka, sementara sang tokoh utama kita meneriakkan nama sang teman. “Awang!” pekiknya. Banyak fans komik Indonesia menyadari bahwa sosok Awang tersebut kelak akan menjadi superhero Godam. Apakah artinya film Godam pun tengah disiapkan? Hmmm…</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53643\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-gundala-tampilkan-asal-usul-sancaka-yang-keras/attachment/05-gundala-trailer/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-gundala-trailer.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-gundala-trailer\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-gundala-trailer.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-gundala-trailer.jpg\" alt=\"Sancaka mendapatkan kekuatan Gundala. Sumber: Screenplay Films\" class=\"wp-image-53643\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-gundala-trailer.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/05-gundala-trailer-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Sancaka mendapatkan kekuatan Gundala. Sumber: Screenplay Films</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Trailer Gundala pun menampilkan informasi tanggal rilis\nfilmnya, yaitu di bulan Agustus 2019. Hmm, waktunya masih banyak ya? Siap-siap\nnabung buat tiket nggak ada salahnya kan? Karena kamu pasti nggak mau\nmelewatkan adaptasi film Gundala yang satu ini!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"678b4e65-9e3b-586d-929b-3df1eacf627e"}}}